page.title: 07WHAT WE EAT
page.content: We eat all sorts of food like Chinese Indian French Italian.Hamburgers and chips which are both junk food from a take-away shop. For breakfast I normally have cereal which consists of wheat barley oats maize and rye.Then I have toast and marmalade. For lunch I have beans or cheese on toast or maybe sandwiches.Then cake or chocolate. For dinner I might have meat with potatoes and vegetables.For pudding I might have tinned fruit or a pie with ice-cream. People usually eat these things. At christmas,people have turkey,roast potatoes,christmas pudding,plums, sweets and things like that. You can have birthday cakes on your birthday with sausages on sticks and special things like that.
